race.comment: SASSY LAD (8) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fifth (23.02) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Key player on best and worth another chance. CANYA TILLY (1) hit the frame after colliding with another runner last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track, finishing a 7 length third (22.94). This tougher but expected to be in the finish. INVESTED (2) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 5.5 lengths into second (17.25) at Northam in a Free For All over 297m. Expected to feature again. GO GETTEM TILLY (6) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.
